# VHS tape for LinkedIn demo - Processing 5 issues with FOAAS MCP Server
# Optimized for LinkedIn: 1200x675 (16:9 aspect ratio)
# Install VHS: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Run: vhs docs/demo/linkedin-demo.tape

# LinkedIn-optimized settings
Output linkedin-demo.gif
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 675
Set FontSize 14
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 15

# Start fresh
Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

# Title card
Type "# 🔥 FOAAS MCP Server - Responding to Issues with Style"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "# Processing 5 bug reports from GitHub..."
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Clear and start processing
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

